query:
SELECT EXISTS(
                SELECT 1
                FROM workspace_members wm
                INNER JOIN role_permissions rp ON wm.role_id = rp.role_id
                INNER JOIN permissions p ON rp.permission_id = p.id
                WHERE wm.workspace_team_id = $1 AND wm.user_id = $2 AND p.key = $3
            ) as "exists!: bool"
